00:20:53.403 --> 00:20:54.823
Mm-hmm. Sure are.

540
00:20:54.900 --> 00:20:57.585
That's not as impressive
as my loose tooth. See?

541
00:20:59.309 --> 00:21:00.653
Ok. ok. you two.

542
00:21:00.769 --> 00:21:02.186
Our deal was that
you could stay awake

543
00:21:02.263 --> 00:21:03.336
until Daddy came home.

544
00:21:03.451 --> 00:21:05.292
Now say good night.

545
00:21:05.407 --> 00:21:07.480
Dad.
do we have to?

546
00:21:11.353 --> 00:21:12.541
No. you two can stay up.

547
00:21:12.657 --> 00:21:14.998
We're just gonna be sittin'
here tellin' each other

548
00:21:15.113 --> 00:21:16.414
