549
00:21:16.491 --> 00:21:17.451
Right. honey?

550
00:21:18.640 --> 00:21:19.521
- Ew!
- Blecch!

551
00:21:19.636 --> 00:21:20.481
Good night.

552
00:21:21.594 --> 00:21:23.856
So what did
the emperor want?

553
00:21:23.971 --> 00:21:24.816
Ahem.

554
00:21:24.931 --> 00:21:26.810
You know what?
He couldn't see me.

555
00:21:26.886 --> 00:21:27.846
Couldn't see you?

556
00:21:27.923 --> 00:21:29.266
