- I don't know.

557
00:21:29.381 --> 00:21:30.606
Well. that's
just rude.

558
00:21:30.721 --> 00:21:31.949
Well. he is
the emperor.

559
00:21:32.064 --> 00:21:32.907
I'm sure he's busy.

560
00:21:33.022 --> 00:21:34.097
No. no. no. no. No.

561
00:21:34.212 --> 00:21:36.397
Emperor or no emperor.
it's called common courtesy.

562
00:21:36.474 --> 00:21:37.434
Honey...

563
00:21:37.549 --> 00:21:38.968
