Sorry to slow you down.

584
00:22:43.134 --> 00:22:44.439
Heh heh heh.

585
00:22:51.803 --> 00:22:52.914
Huh?

586
00:22:55.522 --> 00:22:56.404
Whoa.

587
00:22:56.481 --> 00:22:59.319
