- Shh!

619
00:23:57.849 --> 00:23:59.881
What happened?

620
00:23:59.996 --> 00:24:02.298
I'm tryin' to
figure that out. ok?

621
00:24:04.636 --> 00:24:05.672
Ohh-ho!

622
00:24:05.787 --> 00:24:06.977
I can't remember.

623
00:24:07.092 --> 00:24:08.549
I can't remember
anything.

624
00:24:08.664 --> 00:24:09.892
Wait a minute.

625
00:24:10.007 --> 00:24:11.617
