sense of direction.

684
00:26:19.336 --> 00:26:20.718
Ok. where am I?

685
00:26:23.211 --> 00:26:25.434
Wha--

686
00:26:25.549 --> 00:26:27.352
Help me!
Help me!

687
00:26:27.429 --> 00:26:28.963
Help me!

688
00:26:30.766 --> 00:26:31.611
Uhh.

689
00:26:31.726 --> 00:26:33.220
Too late.

690
00:26:33.297 --> 00:26:35.867
Ok. that was the freakiest
thing I've ever seen.

691
00:26:41.121 --> 00:26:42.847
Aah!

692
00:26:42.962 --> 00:26:44.919
Hmm.
What do you want?

693
00:26:47.028 --> 00:26:48.369
Oh. for me?

694
00:26:48.446 --> 00:26:49.751
Why. I don't know
what to say.

695
00:26:51.632 --> 00:26:52.628
Ow!

696
00:26:52.743 --> 00:26:53.701
Hit the road. bucky.

697
00:26:57.230 --> 00:26:59.071
Aah! Ow!

698
00:26:59.186 --> 00:27:00.451
Huh?

699
00:27:00.567 --> 00:27:01.411
Huh?

700
00:27:03.482 --> 00:27:04.365
Huh?

701
00:27:05.439 --> 00:27:06.397
Uh-oh.

702
00:27:14.605 --> 00:27:16.101
No. no.
No. no. no. no.

703
00:27:17.175 --> 00:27:18.096
No. no.
No. don't.

704
00:27:23.848 --> 00:27:24.923
Ha!

705
00:27:26.380 --> 00:27:28.374
Aah!

706
00:27:30.022 --> 00:27:31.058
No!

707
00:27:37.617 --> 00:27:38.769
Aah!

708
00:27:41.183 --> 00:27:43.217
Aah!

709
