712
00:28:01.589 --> 00:28:03.467
Aah!

713
00:28:09.605 --> 00:28:10.487
Aah!

714
00:28:12.865 --> 00:28:14.017
Yee-aah!

715
00:28:14.132 --> 00:28:16.240
Aah!

716
00:28:16.317 --> 00:28:18.118
Don't worry.
Your Highness. I gotcha.

717
00:28:18.195 --> 00:28:19.192
You're safe now.

718
00:28:22.875 --> 00:28:25.597
Maybe I'm just new to
this whole rescuing thing.

719
00:28:25.712 --> 00:28:27.019
but this. to me.

720
00:28:27.134 --> 00:28:28.858
