change me back.

764
00:30:38.803 --> 00:30:40.259
and then I'll start
construction

765
00:30:40.375 --> 00:30:41.756
on Kuzcotopia.

766
00:30:41.871 --> 00:30:42.714
Oh. yeah.

767
00:30:42.829 --> 00:30:44.670
Ok. now. look.

768
00:30:44.746 --> 00:30:47.048
I think we got off
on the wrong foot here.

769
00:30:47.125 --> 00:30:48.353
