just for you.

778
00:31:02.351 --> 00:31:04.998
And that's...

779
00:31:05.113 --> 00:31:05.957
bad?

780
00:31:06.071 --> 00:31:08.413
Well. yeah.

781
00:31:08.490 --> 00:31:10.789
Nobody's
that heartless.

782
00:31:10.866 --> 00:31:11.787
Mmm.

783
00:31:13.012 --> 00:31:13.971
Now take me back.

784
00:31:14.086 --> 00:31:14.970
What?
Wait. wait.

785
00:31:15.047 --> 00:31:16.619
