back to the palace.

799
00:31:39.708 --> 00:31:41.740
Looks to me like
you're stuck out here.

800
00:31:41.855 --> 00:31:42.968
because unless
you change your mind.

801
00:31:43.084 --> 00:31:45.384
I'm not taking you back.

802
00:31:47.455 --> 00:31:48.913
Because unless
you change your mind.

803
00:31:49.028 --> 00:31:50.333
I'm not
taking you back.

804
